data.description: Country living in Cascade Valley! It begins with great curb appeal and this 1.5+ acre property keeps going! Outside you'll find low maintenance landscape, 2 sheds, lots of parking and a paved circular drive. The garage has one extra deep bay for more storage and radiant floor heat. Inside offers vaulted and 10' ceilings, spacious living room with propane fireplace, huge updated kitchen with loads of countertop, cabinet space and SS appliances, family room downstairs with a pellet stove, radiant floor heat and wet bar. There are 4 bedrooms and 2.75 baths, including a primary suite. Make a plan to see it today!
